     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet ATCDMPN</b></p><a name=\"ATCDMPN\"> </a><a name=\"hcATCDMPN\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/ATC</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-B01AC06\">B01AC06</a></td><td>Acetylsalicylsyre (ASA)</td><td>B01AC06 - acetylsalicylic acid</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L01XX35\">L01XX35</a></td><td>Anagrelide</td><td>L01XX35 - anagrelide</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L01AB01\">L01AB01</a></td><td>Busulfan (Myleran)</td><td>L01AB01 - busulfan</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L01XX05\">L01XX05</a></td><td>Hydroxcarbamid</td><td>L01XX05 - hydroxycarbamide</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-C10AA\">C10AA</a></td><td>Statiner</td><td>C10AA - HMG CoA reductase inhibitors</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L01XH\">L01XH</a></td><td>HDAC hæmmer</td><td>L01XH - Histone deacetylase (HDAC) inhibitors</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L03AB\">L03AB</a></td><td>Interferon</td><td>L03AB - Interferons</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L01EJ01\">L01EJ01</a></td><td>Ruxolitinib</td><td>L01EJ01 - ruxolitinib</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-L04AA\">L04AA</a></td><td>JAK-2 inhibitorer</td><td>L04AA - Selective immunosuppressants</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-ATC.html#ATC-B01A\">B01A</a></td><td>Anden blodfortyndende behandling</td><td>B01A - ANTITHROMBOTIC AGENTS</td></tr></table></li><